{"lang":"fr","stage":7,"title":"fuller sentences","sentences":[{"t":"Il cherche du boulot depuis mars.","en":"He's been looking for a job since March.","a":"n_f75a51c2c76e.mp3"},{"t":"Ça fait trente euros en tout.","en":"It all comes to thirty euros.","a":"n_9ff4d3e1e31c.mp3"},{"t":"On mange à une heure.","en":"We eat at one.","a":"n_c208181eec90.mp3"},{"t":"Je finis à cinq heures.","en":"I finish at five.","a":"n_9e43edf73f93.mp3"},{"t":"Le dimanche je dors beaucoup.","en":"On Sundays I sleep a lot.","a":"n_699954c7001b.mp3"},{"t":"Je travaille pas le samedi.","en":"I don't work on Saturday.","a":"n_fe33a99003da.mp3"},{"t":"À jeudi.","en":"See you on Thursday.","a":"n_b88fa86e7150.mp3"},{"t":"On commence à quelle heure ?","en":"What time do we start?","a":"n_f84098558781.mp3"},{"t":"Aujourd'hui c'est mon anniversaire.","en":"Today is my birthday.","a":"n_959543da73b7.mp3"},{"t":"T'es encore en retard.","en":"You're late again.","a":"n_a0825eeac8d7.mp3"},{"t":"Les deux, ça fait combien ?","en":"How much are the two of them?","a":"n_da0da684974b.mp3"},{"t":"Tu le vends combien ?","en":"How much are you selling it for?","a":"n_a55d22deb76b.mp3"},{"t":"C'est gratuit aujourd'hui.","en":"Getting in is free today.","a":"n_7f7d4c576f43.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal au ventre.","en":"My stomach hurts.","a":"n_aea27d2249f8.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal au dos.","en":"My back hurts.","a":"n_ebc40196ed21.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal aux yeux.","en":"My eyes hurt.","a":"n_116d42a753e1.mp3"},{"t":"Je te présente Ana.","en":"Let me introduce you to Ana.","a":"n_e4c955a68d1c.mp3"},{"t":"Je m'ennuie à la maison.","en":"I'm bored at home.","a":"n_4d8470a09433.mp3"},{"t":"Elle a besoin de plus d'argent.","en":"She needs more money.","a":"n_3ead41e2832b.mp3"},{"t":"Je peux le voir plus tard.","en":"I can see it later.","a":"n_a17f6ec50119.mp3"},{"t":"Tu viens ou tu restes ?","en":"Are you coming or staying?","a":"n_b753cae25ece.mp3"},{"t":"Elle prépare le dîner.","en":"She's making dinner.","a":"n_515135f11e70.mp3"},{"t":"Je pose juste une petite question.","en":"I'll ask a quick question.","a":"n_757801d75156.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai préparé mon sac hier soir.","en":"I packed my bag last night.","a":"n_e36d66e4575c.mp3"},{"t":"Me fais pas rire.","en":"Don't make me laugh.","a":"n_feafc6b1aeff.mp3"},{"t":"Je te raconterai plus tard.","en":"I'll tell you about it later.","a":"n_b95c732a95ad.mp3"},{"t":"Qui te l'a dit ?","en":"Who told you?","a":"n_217f705a0ee9.mp3"},{"t":"Tu me dis jamais rien.","en":"You never tell me anything.","a":"n_6eaf8e2cf920.mp3"},{"t":"Je connais pas ce resto.","en":"I don't know that restaurant.","a":"n_a2c2d44be374.mp3"},{"t":"Je vois pas la différence.","en":"I don't see the difference.","a":"n_fbc45713d3a4.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux te montrer un truc.","en":"I want to show you something.","a":"n_36c6762f2581.mp3"},{"t":"Me regarde pas comme ça.","en":"Don't look at me like that.","a":"n_c990c69bbe0b.mp3"},{"t":"On bosse beaucoup cette semaine.","en":"We're working a lot this week.","a":"n_14f3d640f9e7.mp3"},{"t":"Tu peux me passer le pain ?","en":"Can you pass me the bread?","a":"n_4037ac4e7388.mp3"},{"t":"Mes amis habitent à côté.","en":"My friends live nearby.","a":"n_243649798eb2.mp3"},{"t":"On commence à quatre heures.","en":"We start at four.","a":"n_f594ea05765b.mp3"},{"t":"Il fait froid en décembre.","en":"It's cold in December.","a":"n_9dcb579aba70.mp3"},{"t":"Ma montre est pas à l'heure.","en":"My watch is wrong.","a":"n_7f4fff37b405.mp3"},{"t":"Je t'expliquerai plus tard.","en":"I'll explain later.","a":"n_7f0c28159d28.mp3"},{"t":"Je me suis levé tard aujourd'hui.","en":"I got up late today.","a":"n_a1200cbc4e8f.mp3"},{"t":"T'es pile à l'heure.","en":"You're right on time.","a":"n_27a2c52a64f5.mp3"},{"t":"Je peux payer par carte ?","en":"Can I pay by card?","a":"n_21eefda8c48d.mp3"},{"t":"J'arrête le taxi où ?","en":"Where do I stop the taxi?","a":"n_fb1e92630e10.mp3"},{"t":"Je rate toujours le train.","en":"I always miss the train.","a":"n_3c565e27dc24.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal à une dent.","en":"One of my teeth hurts.","a":"n_49a075773aec.mp3"},{"t":"Hier je suis allé au ciné.","en":"Yesterday I went to the movies.","a":"n_2313cbd0c779.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal aux pieds.","en":"My feet hurt.","a":"n_ff329aa920f6.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde-toi dans le miroir.","en":"Look at yourself in the mirror.","a":"n_173ea327cf36.mp3"},{"t":"Je l'ai jamais essayé.","en":"I've never tried it.","a":"n_33e970adceb9.mp3"},{"t":"T'es allé où samedi ?","en":"Where did you go on Saturday?","a":"n_7f8fafe8ef24.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois manger un truc.","en":"You have to eat something.","a":"n_ab94f84dd7f9.mp3"},{"t":"Non, c'est pas moi.","en":"No, that's not me.","a":"n_fd95202fd410.mp3"},{"t":"Ça va, et toi ?","en":"I'm good, and you?","a":"n_b9f711425912.mp3"},{"t":"Je fais ce que je veux.","en":"I do what I want.","a":"n_64ba3dec4258.mp3"},{"t":"Je fais ce que je peux.","en":"I do what I can.","a":"n_b8296f8b3a78.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois dormir plus.","en":"You have to sleep more.","a":"n_1c776004030d.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois travailler demain ?","en":"Do you have to work tomorrow?","a":"n_98c99e8a5f95.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde ce que j'ai.","en":"Look what I've got.","a":"n_575c9aec512d.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, ça fait mal ici.","en":"Yes, it hurts here.","a":"n_60481e1b8962.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis crevé mais content.","en":"I'm tired but happy.","a":"n_b7f452147a7d.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai faim, je dois manger.","en":"I'm hungry, I need to eat.","a":"n_3ba05024ba77.mp3"},{"t":"Je me lève et je mange.","en":"I get up and eat.","a":"n_700238c83d8c.mp3"},{"t":"Je voudrais commander, s'il te plaît.","en":"I'd like to order, please.","a":"n_3c439ad7bb08.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais que t'as raison.","en":"I know you're right.","a":"n_dfab4019fa4f.mp3"},{"t":"Je crois que t'as raison.","en":"I think you're right.","a":"n_7c699df13d88.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde, c'est Carlos.","en":"Look, this is Carlos.","a":"n_f2617e1ff864.mp3"},{"t":"Je dois étudier aujourd'hui.","en":"I have to study today.","a":"n_4df6f4e53569.mp3"},{"t":"Non, c'est bon.","en":"No, that's fine.","a":"n_416e82836b58.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai besoin de rien, merci.","en":"I don't need anything, thanks.","a":"n_7b3527df6bbe.mp3"},{"t":"Merci, c'est très loin ?","en":"Thanks, is it very far?","a":"n_791ebb0c1a03.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais que je peux le faire.","en":"I know I can do it.","a":"n_f18498613a81.mp3"},{"t":"Tu peux le faire, je le sais.","en":"You can do it, I know it.","a":"n_24665832661f.mp3"},{"t":"Je préfère le faire seul, merci.","en":"I'd rather do it alone, thanks.","a":"n_accb3b38d019.mp3"},{"t":"Je travaille et après je mange.","en":"I work and then eat.","a":"n_3d5d17490bd3.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, elle s'appelle Ana.","en":"Yes, her name is Ana.","a":"n_89bd379552d1.mp3"},{"t":"Faut qu'on parte maintenant.","en":"We have to leave now.","a":"n_5fcedc69a9e2.mp3"},{"t":"On doit tous y aller ?","en":"Do we all have to go?","a":"n_287fb88d4548.mp3"},{"t":"T'as raison, je dois me reposer.","en":"You're right, I need to rest.","a":"n_366ca7fa5c35.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois voir ça.","en":"You have to see this.","a":"n_42bb6dafa2a9.mp3"},{"t":"L'addition, s'il te plaît.","en":"The check, please.","a":"n_94deb03fdfe9.mp3"},{"t":"Non, je suis du Mexique.","en":"No, I'm from Mexico.","a":"n_9bd65b15f391.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, c'est mon amie.","en":"Yes, she's my friend.","a":"n_76909842f345.mp3"},{"t":"Ouais, j'ai vraiment faim.","en":"Yeah, I'm really hungry.","a":"n_165569338698.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mangé plus que toi.","en":"I ate more than you.","a":"n_77aad420141c.mp3"},{"t":"Salut, je m'appelle Carlos.","en":"Hi, my name is Carlos.","a":"n_87461ef1436f.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois être patient.","en":"You need to have patience.","a":"n_18f1144f51c2.mp3"},{"t":"Dis-lui que j'arrive.","en":"Tell him I'm on my way.","a":"n_3dac495f0ca1.mp3"},{"t":"Dis-lui que je suis désolé.","en":"Tell him I'm sorry.","a":"n_5fa47b8f260a.mp3"},{"t":"Enchanté, je suis Carlos.","en":"Nice to meet you, I'm Carlos.","a":"n_2ce0cf90a43b.mp3"},{"t":"Enchantée, je m'appelle Ana.","en":"Nice to meet you, my name is Ana.","a":"n_0ffa701f0937.mp3"},{"t":"Je dois te dire un truc.","en":"I have to tell you something.","a":"n_e0c2399e9b1b.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde ici, pas là.","en":"Look here, not there.","a":"n_4028db62611d.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai trop payé, je sais.","en":"I paid too much, I know.","a":"n_8c4d63607eb5.mp3"},{"t":"Je crois que j'ai de la fièvre.","en":"I think I have a fever.","a":"n_0da7f0652216.mp3"}]}